title: Advantest to Showcase Latest Test Solutions at SEMICON Japan 2025 in Tokyo
description: TOKYO, Dec. 15, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Leading semiconductor test equipment supplier Advantest Corporation (TSE: 6857) will feature its latest semiconductor test solutions at SEMICON Japan 2025, which will be held from Dec. 17-19 at the Tokyo Big Sight in Tokyo, Japan. At this year’s event, Advantest will highlight its broad portfolio of leading-edge test technologies for applications such as AI and high-performance computing (HPC), advanced memory, power electronics, automotive, and wireless communications.
